msgctxt "sn17.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 4. Catutthavagga → saṅghabhedavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Catutthavagga"
msgstr "4. The Fourth Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 31. Bhindisutta → saṅghabhedasuttaṃ (bj) | chindi (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Bhindisutta"
msgstr "31. Schism"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.240"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.31:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.31:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

msgctxt "sn17.31:1.3"
msgid ""
"Lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūto pariyādiṇṇacitto, bhikkhave, devadatto "
"saṃghaṃ bhindi."
msgstr ""
"Devadatta caused a schism in the Saṅgha because his mind was overcome and "
"overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "sn17.31:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.31:1.5"
msgid "sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.31:1.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
